</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ubluebuttmonkey.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Blue butt monkey</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>The HuNgrY MoNkEy <img src=http://www.brellserilis.net/images/goldstartr.gif align=middle></span><br>  Posts: 882<br> <font color=#CC9900>(5/18/01 7:57:04 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.webdeveloper.com/animations/bnifiles/run_cat.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: How much does taunt &quot;taunt&quot; ?</span><hr size=1> From what I can understand, no matter where you are on aggro list, if you success your taunt (on the skill check and lvl check), youll get on top of the hate list.  <p><center>
